<div class="com-share" data-id="10359" data-title="《华伦天奴纽约旗舰店换新颜，塔钟与楼梯是焦点》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10359/medium/10359.jpg?1436649459" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10359.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
